descriptionHtml:
This is a tutorial on how to get my female body.


!!!!!!!!!!INSTALLATION!!!!!!!!!!
First install CBBE v3 with Curvy body, Automatic Textures, CBBE face pack, and BodySlide. Once you have it installed, Go to your Skyrim Data Folder and select "CalientesTools". Open it, and open BodySlide.

The .rar file I have uploaded will contain the presets and values for the slider amounts (The Numbers at the end of the slides) Copy all of those into their spots, go to SAVE PRESET, and type in the name of your choosing. Then, when it is saved, Click the CREATE BODY button, and enjoy.

!!!!!!!IMAGES!!!!!!!!
You may upload all images of this mod in action as you please, without my permission.

Hope this helps you all,

EP1CPH1L
